    <item>
      <title>Pain relieved by Vitamin D if trial lasted more than 5 months (endometriosis, 50K weekly for 12 months)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/pain-relieved-by-vitamin-d-if-trial-lasted-more-than-5-months-endometriosis-50k-weekly-for-12-months/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Aug 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/pain-relieved-by-vitamin-d-if-trial-lasted-more-than-5-months-endometriosis-50k-weekly-for-12-months/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Another endometriosis-related pain trial lasting only 3 months did not result in a benefit.It takes at least 5 months for vitamin D dosing to fully respond without a loading doseLoading doses, on the other hand, result in a response/benefit in &amp;lt; 1 month&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;nav id=&#34;TableOfContents&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#antioxidant-vitamins-supplementation-reduce-endometriosis-related-pelvic-pain-in-humans-a-systematic-review-and-meta-analysis&#34;&gt;Antioxidant vitamins supplementation reduce endometriosis related pelvic pain in humans: a systematic review and meta-analysis&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#see-also-in-vitamindwiki---a-hrefpostsendometriosis-treated-and-perhaps-prevented-by-vitamin-d-many-studies-stylecolor-red-text-decoration-underline-titlethis-postcategory-does-not-exist-yet-endometriosis-treated-and-perhaps-prevented-by-vitamin-d---many-studiesendometriosis-treated-and-perhaps-prevented-by-vitamin-d---many-studiesa&#34;&gt;See also in VitaminDWiki - &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/endometriosis-treated-and-perhaps-prevented-by-vitamin-d-many-studies&#34; style=&#34;color: red; text-decoration: underline;&#34; title=&#34;This post/category does not exist yet: Endometriosis treated, and perhaps prevented, by vitamin D - many studies&#34;&gt;Endometriosis treated, and perhaps prevented, by vitamin D - many studies&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/nav&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;antioxidant-vitamins-supplementation-reduce-endometriosis-related-pelvic-pain-in-humans-a-systematic-review-and-meta-analysis&#34;&gt;Antioxidant vitamins supplementation reduce endometriosis related pelvic pain in humans: a systematic review and meta-analysis&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Reproductive Biology and Endocrinology Vol 21, # 79 (2023) &lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1186/s12958-023-01126-1&#34;&gt;https://doi.org/10.1186/s12958-023-01126-1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
