    <item>
      <title>Large dose Vitamin D before surgery was found to help by 35 studies</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/large-dose-vitamin-d-before-surgery-was-found-to-help-by-35-studies/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 May 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/large-dose-vitamin-d-before-surgery-was-found-to-help-by-35-studies/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:orange;&#34;&gt;This small study would probably have gotten statistically significant results if they have given the 300,000 IU of Vitamin D 3 days BEFORE the surgery. It takes several days for oral vitamin D to get to the cells (injection is slower, nanoemulsion is faster)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;nav id=&#34;TableOfContents&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#optimal-vitamin-d-status-at-admission-appears-to-improve-survival-after-craniotomy-in-patients-with-brain-malignancies&#34;&gt;Optimal vitamin D status at admission appears to improve survival after craniotomy in patients with brain malignancies&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/nav&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;optimal-vitamin-d-status-at-admission-appears-to-improve-survival-after-craniotomy-in-patients-with-brain-malignancies&#34;&gt;Optimal vitamin D status at admission appears to improve survival after craniotomy in patients with brain malignancies&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Clinical Nutrition ESPEN Vol 55, June 2023, Pages 428-433 &lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.1016/j.clnesp.2023.04.009&#34;&gt;https://doi.org/10.1016/j.clnesp.2023.04.009&lt;/a&gt; $25 paywall&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
